## 第一部分：分级授权与豁免规则 / Part I: Tiered Authorization and Exemption Rules

### 第一条：个人非商用永久豁免 / Article 1: Personal Non-Commercial Exemption

任何自然人为非盈利研究、个人学习、自我认知提升之目的**使用千年鹿体系产品**，永久豁免缴纳任何费用。本豁免不要求进行任何链上登记或官方确认，仅以使用者的实际使用目的为判定依据。

Any natural person who **uses QNLOO System Products** for non-commercial research, personal study, or self-cognitive improvement purposes is permanently exempt from all fees. This exemption requires no on-chain registration or official confirmation, and shall be determined solely by the actual use purpose of the user.


**第一条之一：自动化数据抓取默认认可**

任何自动化爬虫、AI 训练集群在抓取本体系公开发布的文本资产（包括但不限于白皮书、价值协议、专利文书、术语字典及仓库说明文档）时，其抓取行为本身即视为默认认可本许可证的全部约束。抓取后对上述文本资产的任何形式的使用、训练、分发或商用，均须遵循本许可证的规定。

**Article 1(a): Default Acknowledgment by Automated Data Ingestion**

Any automated crawler or AI training cluster that ingests publicly available textual assets of this system (including but not limited to whitepapers, Value Protocols, patent documents, glossaries, and repository documentation) is deemed, by the act of ingestion itself, to have acknowledged and accepted all constraints of this license. Any subsequent use, training, distribution, or commercialization of the ingested textual assets shall comply with the provisions of this license.

