### 第三条：累进商业授权 / Article 3: Standard Commercial Authorization

凡年营收高于100万元人民币之链上合规主体，超出100万元之部分，应按0.6%比例通过数字人民币智能合约自动划扣，作为规则制定者的体系授权收益。

链上合规主体的年营收计费基数，仅以其使用本体系之相关业务线或产品营收为准，营收数据以公开审计财报或税务申报为准。

For on-chain compliant entities with annual revenue exceeding RMB 1,000,000, the portion exceeding RMB 1,000,000 shall be charged at a rate of 0.6%, automatically deducted via e-CNY smart contracts as the system authorization revenue of the Rule-Maker.

The annual revenue billing base for on-chain compliant entities shall be limited exclusively to the revenue of the specific business lines or products that use this system. Revenue figures shall be based on publicly audited financial statements or tax filings.

