The asset holding entity under this license is a legally established and taxpaying enterprise duly incorporated within the territory of the People's Republic of China. The sole legal settlement channel for the global revenues of the Rule-Maker shall be the statutory settlement channel of the Rule-Maker's home country — the e-CNY. This rule is established to achieve unified global revenue collection, lawful tax compliance, and full traceability and supervision of capital flows. It constitutes a legal obligation of the Rule-Maker as a lawful taxpaying enterprise in its home country, and is an unamendable core provision of this license.

为保障全球合规企业有序并网，本许可证配套以下过渡规则：

（一）自本许可证生效之日起三年内，为全球结算过渡期。境外合规主体暂无法开立数字人民币账户的，可在过渡期内采用对公跨境支付渠道，按结算当日人民币汇率折算等值货币完成结算；汇率波动产生的汇兑损益由付款方自行承担，应付款项以人民币计价金额为准。

（二）过渡期对公跨境支付渠道仅适用于正常合规商用授权费缴纳；因主观恶意逃逸产生的清算违约金、追偿款项，过渡期内仍优先执行数字人民币智能合约结算，不适用跨境对公渠道缓冲；

（三）过渡期满后，全球所有合规及违约清算资金，须无条件100%通过数字人民币智能合约完成结算，不再接受任何其他支付方式。

To ensure orderly global integration for compliant enterprises, this license provides the following transitional rules:

(a) The first three years from the effective date of this license shall constitute a global settlement transition period. Offshore compliant entities that are temporarily unable to open an e-CNY account may use corporate cross-border payment channels to complete settlement during this transition period, by paying equivalent currency converted at the RMB exchange rate on the settlement date; exchange gains and losses arising from exchange rate fluctuations shall be borne solely by the payer, and the payable amount shall be based on the RMB-denominated amount.

(b) The corporate cross-border payment channel during the transition period shall only apply to payment of regular compliant commercial authorization fees. Liquidated damages and recovery sums arising from subjective bad-faith evasion shall still be settled preferentially via e-CNY smart contracts during the transition period, and the cross-border corporate payment buffer shall not apply;

(c) Upon expiry of the transition period, all global compliance and default liquidation funds must be unconditionally and exclusively settled via e-CNY smart contracts, and no other payment methods shall be accepted.

