针对本体系文本、逻辑架构等非专利作品资产的侵权判定，适用各法域著作权法下的实质性相似判定标准。

在欧盟法域内适用本许可时，需自动对齐欧盟通用数据保护条例及相关主权数据资产确权规范。各生态节点有权针对特定属地法域附加合规附签。

相关诉讼的管辖规则与诉讼主体资格，适用本许可第九条之约定。

For infringement determination of the system's granted patents, the Doctrine of Equivalents shall be strictly followed in jurisdictions of the United States. Any commercial product that substantially replicates the patented core technical architectures such as three-layer separation and edge auditing, or the complete causal cognitive logic chain of this system, shall be subject to the liquidated damages provisions of this license regardless of upper-layer code reconstruction. Generic business processes and unpatented general architectural ideas are not covered by these restrictions.

For infringement determination of non-patent work assets such as the system's textual content and logical architectures, the substantial similarity standard under the copyright law of each jurisdiction shall apply.

When this license is applied within the jurisdictions of the European Union, it shall automatically align with the General Data Protection Regulation and related sovereign data asset confirmation norms. Ecosystem nodes have the right to attach additional jurisdictional compliance schedules for specific territories.

The jurisdiction rules and litigation standing for relevant lawsuits shall be subject to Article 9 of this license.

### 第八条：赏金权利预先让渡 / Article 8: Pre-Assignment of Bounty Rights

凡未完成生态合规并网、未履行缴费义务之主体，本许可证之所有权人特此作出不可撤销之权利让渡安排：针对侵权违约产生的赔付款项，超出0.6%基准授权费的溢价部分，全部让渡给举证成功的吹哨人，作为其维权激励。

本安排仅为收益权利的预先处分，不构成对诉讼行为的委托授权；资产持有主体可配合符合属地法律要求的维权主体履行必要的权利证明手续，该等配合不视为对诉讼行为的指示、担保或连带责任承诺。

For any entity that has not completed ecological compliance integration and has failed to fulfill its payment obligations, the owner of this license hereby makes an irrevocable right assignment arrangement: the premium portion of infringement breach compensation exceeding the 0.6% benchmark authorization fee shall be fully assigned to the Qui Tam Relator who successfully provides evidence as their enforcement incentive.

This arrangement is merely a pre-disposition of revenue rights and does not constitute a commissioned authorization for litigation actions. The asset holding entity may cooperate with enforcement parties meeting local legal requirements to complete necessary right certification formalities, and such cooperation shall not be deemed as instruction, guarantee, or assumption of joint liability for litigation actions.

