### 第九条：吹哨人诉讼资格 / Article 9: Qui Tam Standing

**取证与悬赏（全球适用）**

全球任何极客、律所或第三方机构（以下统称「吹哨人」，英文对应 **Qui Tam Relator**），通过开源分发之主权取证工具包，在网络层或代码层成功捕获并向分布式账本存证侵权特征指纹（包括但不限于0xABCD特征字、零宽隐藏水印、语法偏差水印等），自动获得对应溢价部分的赏金请求权，具体分配比例与规则按本许可证第十条、第十二条执行。

主权取证工具包禁止一切侵入式主动探测，仅被动接收、分析公开可访问网络端口之出站流量特征，严格遵循属地网络安全与数据隐私法规。

**Evidence Collection & Bounty (Globally Applicable)**

Any geek, law firm, or third-party organization worldwide (hereinafter collectively referred to as the "**Qui Tam Relator**") that successfully captures, through the open-source distributed Sovereign Forensic Toolkit, and records on the distributed ledger pre-existing infringement fingerprints (including but not limited to 0xABCD feature flags, zero-width hidden watermarks, grammatical deviation watermarks, etc.) shall automatically obtain the right to claim the corresponding premium portion bounty. The specific distribution ratio and rules shall be implemented in accordance with Article 10 and Article 12 of this license.

The Sovereign Forensic Toolkit is strictly prohibited from conducting any intrusive active probing. It may only passively receive and analyze egress traffic characteristics from publicly accessible network ports, in strict compliance with local cybersecurity and data privacy regulations.

**诉讼管辖（属地限制）**

任何依据本许可证发起的侵权诉讼，仅可在以下任一法域的法院提起：（一）吹哨人所属国或主要执业地所在国；（二）侵权行为发生地国。
符合上述管辖限制的前提下，各法域诉讼资格规则如下：
- 美国境内司法辖区：取证存证的吹哨人自动取得共同原告资格；
- 中国大陆、欧盟及其余全球法域：原告资格专属资产持有主体或其合法书面授权的律师事务所。

