2.  The remaining premium portion (0.2% of annual revenue for inadvertent omissions, 0.4% of annual revenue for subjective bad faith) shall be paid directly by the infringing entity to the Qui Tam Relator who successfully provides evidence as their enforcement incentive bounty.

All enforcement-related expenses, including evidence collection costs, litigation fees, attorney fees, notarization fees, etc., shall be borne solely by the Qui Tam Relator and covered from the bounty received.

